title: Cowboys-Bears, Dak Prescott, Jerry Jones, coaching, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Cowboys-Bears, Dak Prescott, Jerry Jones, coaching, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses the Cowboys-Bears game, what worries him about Dak Prescott, Jerry Jones' heated radio interview, what is separating average NFL teams from the great ones, and his Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include Rich Ohrnberger, Joel Klatt, Orlando Scandrick, Stanford Routt, and Jason McIntyre.
